# Power BI — versioned as .pbip project (text/JSON, diff-friendly);
# the compiled .pbix is a local convenience copy, not source of truth.
# The .pbi/ folders hold machine-local cache/settings (VertiPaq cache,
# encrypted security bindings) — never meant for source control.
*.pbix
*.pbix.autorecover
**/.pbi/

